      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical and FDA in-house FEA codes operate under documented SQA plans with version control, regression testing, and formal release procedures.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA environments (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) are operated under SQA frameworks consistent with Gradation 2 requirements. Version-controlled input decks and documented solver settings are archived for each analysis run."
