      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario (ASTM F1717 static compression-bending, non-cannulated 7.5 mm construct) is the same scenario as the COU; no extrapolation beyond validated conditions is required.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity is co-extensive with the COU: the same screw design, same loading protocol, same QoIs, and same acceptance bounds are used in both the validation and the regulatory decision context. No extrapolation to different screw diameters, cannulated designs, or dynamic loading conditions is claimed."
